Package: WatchPID
Title: Watches a Linux Process and Notifies Status
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = c("Robert", "M"),
           family = "Flight",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rflight79@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8141-7788"))
Description: Given one or more Linux process ID's (PID), watches to see if
  those processes are active, and if the process dies, notifies
  the user that the process has died.
